(Be aware that her family was totally destroyed in the crash of the 
ship. She is the only surviver.)


::Trinity::
She looked up at Koj and then started jumping around and 
yelling."YIPPY! HOOORAAYYY! YAHHOOOO! MOM AND DAD ARE ALIVE! MOM AND 
DAD ARE ALIVE! WWWAAAHOOOOOO!"  She was just over joyed that her 
parents had lived.  She didn't even notice that her voice carried 
like thunder down the halls of the ship. "WAAAAHOOOOO! MOM AND DAD 
ARE OK!" She roared out in her kitten roar, almost hoping her parents 
heard it and would find her there.
